If running from EC2
 acquire permissions to AWS resources via IAM
 configure default region at ~/.aws/config
  [default]
  region=us-east-1
If running from on-prem
 AWS CLI, ~/.aws/credential, and ~/.aws/config need configuring
  ~/.aws/credential
   [default]
   aws_access_key_id = abc123
   aws_secret_access_key = abc123

CentOS 7 env setup
 sudo yum install -y epel-release
 sudo yum install -y python-pip
 sudo pip install --upgrade pip
 sudo pip install boto3
Then create 'script.py' files and run them with 'python script.py'
Or enter the python interpreter with 'python' then type in the script
